"A “Common dedicated to Transition Facilitation”:

"the Transition Support Consortium (TSC) (or in French CAT, for Consortium d’Accompagnement des Transitions) ... is an alliance or multilateral agreement initiated in November 2022 and formulated in March 2023 to accelerate the change in scale of transitions through support, facilitation and training in collective intelligence using dialogue and generative processes."

(https://pad.lescommuns.org/TSC-General-Presentation_1#)


